<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
<head>

<title>⚔️ Shadows Of Valhalla Login</title>

<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>

<style>

body{
background:linear-gradient(
135deg,
#020617,
#0f172a
);
color:white;
height:100vh;
display:flex;
align-items:center;
justify-content:center;
font-family:sans-serif;
}

.logo{
animation:pulseGlow 2.2s infinite ease-in-out;
}

@keyframes pulseGlow{

0%{
filter:
drop-shadow(
0 0 10px rgba(109,40,217,.4)
);
}

50%{
filter:
drop-shadow(
0 0 28px rgba(109,40,217,.9)
)
drop-shadow(
0 0 48px rgba(76,29,149,.5)
);
}

100%{
filter:
drop-shadow(
0 0 10px rgba(109,40,217,.4)
);
}

}

.card{
background:rgba(30,41,59,.75);
backdrop-filter:blur(14px);
border-radius:20px;
border:1px solid rgba(109,40,217,.35);
padding:45px;
text-align:center;
width:380px;
box-shadow:
0 0 25px rgba(109,40,217,.25);
}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="card">

<img
src="/logo.png"
class="logo w-24 mx-auto mb-6"
/>

<h1
class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-400 mb-6"
>

⚔️ Shadows Of Valhalla ⚔️

</h1>

<p class="text-slate-300 mb-6">

Login with Discord to manage battles,
view the calendar and oversee the agency.

</p>

<div class="flex flex-col gap-4">

<a
href="/login"
class="bg-purple-700 hover px-6 py-3 rounded-xl shadow-lg text-lg transition font-semibold"

>

Login with Discord ⚔️

</a>

<a
href="/calendar"
class="bg-slate-700 hover px-6 py-3 rounded-xl shadow-lg text-lg transition"

>

View Battle Calendar 📅

</a>

</div>

<p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mt-6">

Members can view battles •
Admins manage the agency

</p>

</div>

</body>
</html>
